{"word":"G1608 - ἐκπορνεύω - ekporneúō - ek-porn-yoo'-o - Give self over to fornication","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκπορνεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekporneúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-porn-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Give self over to fornication</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விபசாரம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to go a whoring, \"give oneself over to fornication\""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G4203 - πορνεύω - porneúō - porn-yoo'-o/4203\">G4203</a>; to <i>be utterly unchaste:</i> - give self over to fornication.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1608/1608\">G1608</a>, <a href=\"#/G4202/4202\">G4202</a>, <a href=\"#/G4203/4203\">G4203</a>, <a href=\"#/G4204/4204\">G4204</a>, <a href=\"#/G4205/4205\">G4205</a>"}]}